        <a href="/blog/inflables-jardin-exterior-cdmx/" class="art-sidebar__link">→ Inflables para jardín y exterior</a>
      </div>
      <div class="art-sidebar__box art-sidebar__box--cat">
        <h3 class="art-sidebar__title">🎪 Nuestros inflables</h3>
        <a href="/inflables/gusanitos/" class="art-sidebar__link">→ Gusanitos Tropical</a>
